Package com.model

Record Hit

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.model.Hit
public record Hit(float attackValue, float hitChance)
extends java.lang.Record
This record is used to transmit an attack to a target soldier. It contains the damages that would be caused upon receiving the attack and the chance of it hitting as a multiplier (ex: 1.1).
